{"tid":304417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平:作晚講的「債券通」，是否重大的歷史投資機遇?","createTime":"2017-07-01T01:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T02:15:08.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"173f22e3440e00020adb9e0aa6ab8dda06021953","tid":304417,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:17:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">習近平:作晚講的「債券通」，是否重大的歷史投資機遇?</span><br />\n<br />\n習近平作晚講的「債券通」有冇<span style=\"color: red;\">本金鎖定期</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">匯出限制</span>? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">交易貨幣係咪用人民幣?</span><br />\n<br />\n通過CMU去買，係咪唔同IBOND咁可以網上銀行買賣?<br />\n<br />\n香港IBOND債券<span style=\"color: red;\">係香港中央結算，同承担股票清算交收責任</span>，<br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">「債券通」係咪內地結算</span>?<span style=\"color: red;\">內地銀行承担股票清算交收責任</span>?<br />\n<br />\n因為國內企業要國際化要<span style=\"color: red;\">「一帶一路」</span>加上<br />\n<br />\n人民幣加入SDR，係咪咁所以用「債券通」加速推進?<br />\n<br />\n因為中國債券市場對外開放比較低，<span style=\"color: red;\">國際投資者佔比從開放初期的2%</span><br />\n<br />\n有報導預計至2020年，<span style=\"color: red;\">外資參與中國債市的程度可達10%</span>，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>因此今次是否重大的歷史投資機遇?</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n本身香港人存入銀行既錢，都有唔少借左返大陸，<br />\n<br />\n而家又積極將外匯儲備買人仔債劵， 又送錢返袓國，<br />\n<br />\n不單只係咁，強積金今年有「預設投資」下的基金，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>也可能預設下買了債券。 </ins><ins>令好多人的強積金也不知不覺買下債券。</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n也有不少海外華人有興趣，因為雙房毒債都係推到全球人中招啦，<br />\n<br />\n對歐美債減少了興趣，今次借香港個名，相信比到唔少海外華人信心。<br />\n<br />\n中國銀行間債券市場現佔債市餘額9成，包括國債、企業債、重有地方債，東北債果堆等等。係咪又係所謂國債3厘但鎖你 3-4年到?<br />\n<br />\n咁「債券通」前景如何?"},{"pid":"f2ba9ae2d0b50a001fdc64392efc589e5b5253d5","tid":304417,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b5b0c042aa1b4a61ec2c70df63db112a827cd4","tid":304417,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"債券係咪歷史文件？"},{"pid":"0cd5d58134d8e05b178bdde6fedbf6b76be6170f","tid":304417,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>債券係咪歷史文件？</blockquote><br />\n咩歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bc4af19f14553adcfe6545684690ae9b0baf12","tid":304417,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>債券係咪歷史文件？</blockquote><br />\n咩歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口交部話歷史文件無意義，可以唔算數架"},{"pid":"08075c0d0eda952ddd37df950fe8af90e8c9317b","tid":304417,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>債券係咪歷史文件？</blockquote><br />\n咩歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口交部話歷史文件無意義，可以唔算數架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次用咁香港個朵，習總又話送大禮，一帶一路又係佢重頭戲，細水長流，<br />\n<br />\n可能之後強積金會自動買，港共也有可能用外匯買，大陸債產品同債基發行商唔會突然間收檔吓? 可能係拖住先，又可以唔俾你變現，一直買賣，又吹佢地唔脹喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82f0c6d8d927caadf044a5dc0d5a226ea4058d3","tid":304417,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:47:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">作晚.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2ee5839bbe89959d78d9925dc096997018770c8d","tid":304417,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">習近平:<del>作</del><span style=\"color: red;\">昨</span>晚講的「債券通」，是否重大的歷史投資機遇?</span>"},{"pid":"8486d65118eaa13fd744f37c2ce87ef2f1328e40","tid":304417,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor